lead_paragraph: Jason Bohn says he wanted to go back to his room to take a shower before going to the hospital with chest pains and didn't realize he was having a major heart attack until paramedics at the Honda Classic put him on a stretcher and called for an ambulance.

headline.print_headline: Jason Bohn Thinks He Got 'One Hell of a Mulligan'
